# Template .envrc for Nix flake projects
# Copy this file to your project root as .envrc and run: direnv allow

# Basic flake loading - uses the default devShell
use flake

# Alternative: Load a specific devShell output
# use flake .#myDevShell

# Alternative: Watch additional files for changes (triggers rebuild)
# watch_file flake.lock
# watch_file shell.nix

# Optional: Set additional environment variables
# export MY_VAR="value"

# Optional: Add local bin directory to PATH
# PATH_add bin
